f\u0430\u043c\u2019\u044f\u0442\u0456 \u0421. \u041a. \u041a\u0443\u043b\u044c\u0436\u0438\u043d\u0441\u044c\u043a\u043e\u0433\u043e (1867\u20131943) |url=http://www.vgosau.kiev.ua/load_period-sb/Posulla-2017.pdf |date=2017 |publisher=\u0426\u0435\u043d\u0442\u0440 \u043f\u0430\u043c\u2019\u044f\u0442\u043a\u043e\u0437\u043d\u0430\u0432\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0430 \u041d\u0430\u0446\u0456\u043e\u043d\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u043e\u0457 \u0410\u043a\u0430\u0434\u0435\u043c\u0456\u0457 \u043d\u0430\u0443\u043a \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0457\u043d\u0438 |location=Kiev, Ukraine |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831134922/http://www.vgosau.kiev.ua/load_period-sb/Posulla-2017.pdf |archivedate=31 August 2019 |language=Ukrainian | isbn=978-966-8999-84-0 |trans-title=Earning the Message: Collection of Scientific Works in Memory of S. K. Kulzhynskii(1867\u20131943)}}\n*{{cite journal |ref={{harvid|\u0421\u0443\u043f\u0440\u0443\u043d\u0435\u043d\u043a\u043e|2018}} |last1=\u0421\u0443\u043f\u0440\u0443\u043d\u0435\u043d\u043a\u043e (Suprunenko) |first1= \u041e. \u0411. (O. B.) |title=\u041f\u0430\u043c\u2019\u044f\u0442\u0456 \u0421.\u041a. \u041a\u0443\u043b\u044c\u0436\u0438\u043d\u0441\u044c\u043a\u043e\u0433\u043e |url=https://arheologia.com.ua/index.php/arheologia/article/download/11/11 |journal=\u0410\u0440\u0445\u0435\u043e\u043b\u043e\u0433\u0456\u044f |date=2018 |issue=1 |publisher=Institute of Archaeology of the National Academy of Sciences of Ukraine |location=Kiev, Ukraine |access-date=31 March 2020 |language=Ukrainian |issn=0235-3490 |trans-title=In Memory of S. K. Kulzhinsky}}\n*{{cite book |ref=harv |author=United States Bureau of Labor Statistics |title=Retail Prices, 1913 to December 1920 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GKomAQAAIAAJ&pg=PA48 |year=1922 |publisher=[[U.S. Government Printing Office]] |location=Washington, D. C.}}\n*{{cite book |ref=harv |last=Velychenko |first=Stephen |title=State Building in Revolutionary Ukraine: A Comparative Stu