]]/[[2000 in sports|00]]&nbsp;\u2013 3rd\n*[[2000 in sports|2000]]/[[2001 in sports|01]]&nbsp;\u2013 2nd\n*[[2001 in sports|2001]]/[[2002 in sports|02]]&nbsp;\u2013 9th\n*[[2002 in sports|2002]]/[[2003 in sports|03]]&nbsp;\u2013 6th\n*[[2003 in sports|2003]]/[[2004 in sports|04]]&nbsp;\u2013 '''Champions'''\n*[[2004 in sports|2004]]/[[2005 in sports|05]]&nbsp;\u2013 '''Champions'''\n*[[2005 in sports|2005]]/[[2006 in sports|06]]&nbsp;\u2013 3rd\n*[[2006 in sports|2006]]/[[2007 in sports|07]]&nbsp;\u2013 9th\n*[[2007 in sports|2007]]/[[2008 in sports|08]]&nbsp;\u2013 6th\n*[[2008 in sports|2008]]/[[2009 in sports|09]]&nbsp;\u2013 3rd\n*[[2009 in sports|2009]]/[[2010 in sports|10]]&nbsp;\u2013 3rd\n*[[2010 in sports|2010]]/[[2011 in sports|11]]&nbsp;\u2013 3rd\n*[[2011 in sports|2011]]/[[2012 in sports|12]]&nbsp;\u2013 5th\n*[[2012 in sports|2012]]/[[2013 in sports|13]]&nbsp;\u2013 '''Champions'''\n*[[2013 in sports|2013]]/[[2014 in sports|14]]&nbsp;\u2013 2nd\n*[[2014 in sports|2014]]/[[2015 in sports|15]]&nbsp;\u2212 '''Champions'''\n*[[2015 in sports|2015]]/[[2015 in sports|16]]&nbsp;\u2013 5th\n*[[2016 in sports|2016]]/[[2016 in sports|17]]&nbsp;\u2013 4th\n*[[2017 in sports|2017]]/[[2018 in sports|18]]&nbsp;- 3rd\n*[[2018 in sports|2018]]/[[2019 in sports|19]]&nbsp;\u2013 9th\n* Executive chairman: {{flagicon|South Africa}} '''[[Kaizer Motaung]]'''\n* Football manager: {{flagicon|South Africa}} '''[[Bobby Motaung]]'''\n* Team manager: {{flagicon|South Africa}} '''[[Gerald Sibeko]]'''\n* Coach: {{flagicon|Germany}} '''[[Ernst Middendorp]]'''\n* Assistant coaches: {{flagicon|South Africa}} '''[[Shaun Bartlett]]'''\n* Goalkeeper coach: {{flagicon|Scotland}} '''[[Lee Baxter]]'''\n\n===Premier League Records===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!rowspan=\"2\"|season\n!rowspan=\"2\"|pos\n!colspan=\"9\"|Record\n|-\n!P !! W !! D !! L !! GF !! GA !! GD !! PTS !! win%\n|-\n|-style=\"background:lightblue\"\n|'''[[1996-97 Premier Soccer League|1996-97]]'''||'''2nd'''\n|34\n|18\n|12\n