p Rucker<ref>https://twitter.com/PhilipRucker</ref>\n*''[[The New York Times]]'' \u2013 [[Peter Baker (author)|Peter Baker]], [[Maggie Haberman]], [[Annie Karni]], [[Michael D. Shear]], Al Drago<ref>https://twitter.com/Al_Drago</ref>\n*''[[USA Today]]'' \u2013 David Jackson<ref>https://twitter.com/djusatoday</ref>\n*[[Agence France-Presse]] \u2013 [[Andrew Beatty]], J\u00e9r\u00f4me Cartillier<ref>https://twitter.com/jcartillier</ref>\n*[[McClatchy]] \u2013 Francesca Chambers<ref>https://twitter.com/fran_chambers</ref>, Michael Wilner<ref>https://twitter.com/mawilner</ref>\n*''[[Politico]]'' \u2013 Nancy Cook<ref>https://twitter.com/nancook</ref>, Anita Kumar<ref>https://twitter.com/anitakumar01</ref>\n*Foreign Press \u2013 Yavuz Atalay (''[[Ak\u015fam]]'')<ref>https://twitter.com/_yavuzatalay</ref>, Conrad Chaffee (''[[Tokyo Shimbun]]'')<ref>https://twitter.com/conradchaffee</ref>, J. Jes\u00fas Esquivel (''[[Proceso (magazine)|Proceso]]'')<ref>https://twitter.com/JJesusEsquivel</ref>, Raghubir Goyal (''India Globe'')<ref>http://www.amimagazine.org/2017/08/09/washington-insider-raghubir-goyal-indias-rep-press-pool/</ref>, Lalit Jha ([[Press Trust of India]])<ref>https://twitter.com/lalitkjha</ref>, Luc\u00eda Leal (''[[EFE]]'')<ref>https://twitter.com/lucialealb?lang=en</ref>\n*''[[The Washington Times]]'' \u2013 Dave Boyer<ref>https://twitter.com/DaveBoyer</ref>\n*''[[The Hill (newspaper)|The Hill]]'' \u2013 [[Niall Stanage]]\n*[[Voice of America]] \u2013 [[Steven L. Herman]]\n*[[National Journal]] \u2013 George Condon<ref>https://twitter.com/georgecondon</ref>, Tom DeFrank<ref>https://twitter.com/TomDeFrank</ref>\n*''[[Time]]'' \u2013 Brian Bennett<ref>https://twitter.com/ByBrianBennett</ref>\n*Foreign Press \u2013 [[David Martosko]] (''[[Daily Mail]]''), Demetri Sevastopulo (''[[Financial Times]]'')<ref>https://twitter.com/Dimi</ref>, [[David Smith (journalist)|David Smith]] (''[[The Guardian]]'')\n*Regional Newspapers \u2013 Todd Gillman (''[[Dallas Morning News]]'')<ref>https://twitter.com/toddgillman</ref>, Liz Goodwin (''[[The Boston Globe]]'')<ref>https://twitter.com/lizcgoodwin</ref>, Frank Lockwood (''[[Arkansas Democrat-Gazette]]'')<ref>https://twitter.com/LockwoodFrank</ref>, [[Debra Saunders]] (''[[Las Vegas Review-Journal]]''), Eli Stokols (''[[Los Angeles Times]]'')<ref>https://twitter.com/EliStokols</ref>, [[Lynn Sweet]] (''[[Chicago Sun-Times]]'')\n*[[Real Clear Politics]] \u2013 Carl Cannon<ref>https://twitter.com/CarlCannon</ref>\n*''[[Christian Science Monitor]]'' \u2013 Linda Feldman<ref>https://twitter.com/linda_feldmann</ref>\n*''[[Washington Examiner]]'' \u2013 Katherine Doyle <ref>https://twitter.com/katiadoyl</ref>\n*[[Yahoo! News]] \u2013 [[Hunter Walker]]\n*[[HuffPost]] \u2013 Jennifer Bendery<ref>https://twitter.com/jbendery</ref>\n*''[[Roll Call]]'' \u2013  John T. Bennett<ref>https://twitter.com/BennettJohnT</ref>\n*[[BuzzFeed News]] \u2013 Rosie Gray<ref>https://twitter.com/RosieGray</ref>\n*[[The Daily Beast]] \u2013 Lachlan Markay<ref>https://twitter.com/lachlan</ref>\n*[[Axios (website)|Axios]] \u2013 Alayna Treene<ref>https://twitter.com/alaynatreene</ref>\n*[[Breitbart]] \u2013 Charlie Spiering<ref>https://twitter.com/charliespiering</ref>\n*[[CNSNews.com]] \u2013 Melanie Arter<ref>https://twitter.com/ladaisia</ref>\n*[[The Daily Signal]] \u2013 Fred Lucas<ref>https://twitter.com/FredLucasWH</ref>\n*[[Environment & Energy Publishing]]'' \u2013 Evan Lehmann<ref>https://twitter.com/evanlehmann</ref>\n*''[[Newsweek]]'' \u2013 [[Andrew Feinberg (journalist)|Andrew Feinberg]]\n*''[[Playboy]]'' \u2013 Brian Karem<ref>https://twitter.com/BrianKarem</ref>\n*[[Rick Wiles|TruNews]]<ref>https://www.jpost.com/international/the-white-house-gave-credentials-to-antisemitic-media-615213</ref> \u2013 Edward Szall<ref>https://twitter.com/realEdwardSzall</ref>\n*''[[U.S. News and World Report]]'' \u2013 [[Kenneth T. Walsh]]\n*''[[Washington Blade]]'' \u2013 Chris Johnson<ref>https://twitter.com/chrisjohnson82</ref>\n*AWPS News \u2013 Kristina Anderson <ref>https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/theres-the-major-media-and-then-theres-the-other-white-house-press-corps/2016/02/21/f69c5f92-c460-11e5-8965-0607e0e265ce_story.html</ref><ref>https://twitter.com/AWPSNews</ref>\n*ThePavlovicToday.com \u2013 [[Ksenija Pavlovic]]<ref>https://twitter.com/ksenijapavlovic</ref>\n*WestWingReports.com \u2013 Paul Brandus<ref>https://twitter.com/WestWingReport</ref>\n\n====Radio==== <!-- alphabetize by last name -->\n\n*[[CBS News Radio]] \u2013 [[Mark Knoller]], [[Steven Portnoy]]\n*[[NPR]] \u2013 [[Tamara Keith]], [[Mara Liasson]], Franco Ordo\u00f1ez<ref>https://www.npr.org/people/729411445/franco-ordonez</ref>, Ayesha Rascoe<ref>https://www.npr.org/people/599484393/ayesha-rascoe</ref>, Roberta Rampton<ref>https://www.npr.org/people/778648748/roberta-rampton</ref>\n*[[Associated Press|AP Radio]] \u2013 Sagar Meghani<ref>https://twitter.com/smeghaniap?lang=en</ref>\n*[[American Urban Radio Networks]] \u2013 [[April Ryan]]\n*[[ABC News Radio]] \u2013 Karen Travers<ref>https://twitter.com/karentravers</ref>\n*[[Fox News Radio]] \u2013 [[Jon Decker]]\n*[[Sirius-XM]] \u2013 Oliver Knox<ref>https://twitter.com/OKnox</ref>\n*[[Salem Radio Network]] \u2013 Greg Clugston<ref>https://twitter.com/GregClugstonDC</ref>\n*[[Westwood One News]] \u2013 Bob Costantini<ref>https://twitter.com/CostantiniWW1</ref>\n*Talk Media News<ref>http://www.talkmedianews.com/our-staff/</ref> \u2013 Jon-Christoper Bua<ref>https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/theres-the-major-media-and-then-theres-the-other-white-house-press-corps/2016/02/21/f69c5f92-c460-11e5-8965-0607e0e265ce_story.html</ref>, Doug Christian\n\n===Notable former correspondents=== <!-- alphabetize by last name -->\n{{div col|colwidth=35em}}\n*[[Michael Allen (journalist)|Mike Allen]] \u2013 ''[[Politico (newspaper)|Politico]]''\n*[[Jim Angle]] \u2013 [[National Public Radio]]\n*[[Jim Axelrod]] \u2013 [[CBS News]]\n*[[Bret Baier]] 